{"tid":1950623,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有冇人記得過咗身嘅手足？","createTime":"2020-03-30T12:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T10:05:50.000Z","uid":76332,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a430d99607e3857f595acf8e484a586666196708","tid":1950623,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wHiij_puVNk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwHiij_puVNk&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2RV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=7e3c9c54\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wHiij_puVNk</a><br />\n<br />\n人死不能復生 我做到嘅唔多 唯有寫首歌紀念佢哋 <br />\n提醒自己同其他人 佢哋付出咗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家唔好白廢佢哋心血 繼續行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34a14c0fe61a9c273d850e039ec3fb1f509f818","tid":1950623,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851f28307e6433d1eb9018ffc502c7cbb9134db5","tid":1950623,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7686cd928f051469e205cc80f40b470ad58a553b","tid":1950623,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee40b0d67a162a5bc1e624d9e1ebd85bff53469","tid":1950623,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0854fc79c717aecb548bf55f7aecc5445162351c","tid":1950623,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794590aff7922